# <%= current_jurisdiction.site_title %>

> <%= current_jurisdiction.site_title %> is a source-first civic information site for browsing <%= current_jurisdiction.name %> public meetings, matters, attachments, extracted document text, generated summaries, source links, and theme trends.

Official public records are authoritative. Generated summaries, extracted text, and theme labels are assistive metadata for discovery and should be checked against official source materials before making factual claims.

## Key Pages

- [Homepage and Pulse](<%= root_url %>): Recent agenda activity and theme trends.
- [Meetings](<%= public_meetings_url %>): Public meetings, bodies, agenda items, and source links.
- [Matters](<%= public_matters_url %>): Public matters, files, attachments, extracted text, generated summaries, and related meetings.
- [Data Health](<%= data_url %>): Ingestion freshness, record counts, import coverage, extraction coverage, and known source-data limits.
- [Glossary](<%= glossary_url %>): Civic Gallery terminology and source-system language.
- [Sitemap](<%= sitemap_url %>): Crawlable page inventory for this host.

## Source Boundaries

- Primary source system: <%= current_jurisdiction.ingestion_source_label %> (<%= current_jurisdiction.source_host %>).
- Official source links on matter and meeting pages should be treated as the source of truth.
- Generated summaries and theme classifications are model-derived and may be incomplete or wrong.
- Search snippets and extracted text come from public documents and can contain OCR or extraction errors.

## Suggested Use

Use this site to find relevant official records quickly, then cite the linked official source document or meeting record when accuracy matters.
